    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Press the <strong>torn ciabatta</strong> into the marinade until all the sauce soaks into the bread – these are your<strong> tomatoey croutons</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> tomatoey croutons</strong> to a separate <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined tray with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1655204527885-x200.jpg",
