      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After the initial 10 min, remove the tray from the oven and add the<strong> sliced pepper </strong>to the other side with a small drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a small pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Push the aubergine closer together and tear your <strong>'Nduja </strong>over the top (can’t handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Return the tray to the oven along with the tomatoey croutons for 18-20 min or until the pepper is charred and the croutons are crispy around the edges</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1655204560930-x200.jpg",
