    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel your <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong> until you end up with a pile of cheese shavings</p><p>Grate any <strong>remaining Italian hard cheese </strong>and add it to the basil oil</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry wit kitchen paper</p><p>Remove the tray with the aubergine from the oven and break the 'Nduja up with a spatula, then mix through the aubergine wedges until they are coated in the spicy oil – this is your<strong> 'Nduja graffiti aubergine</strong></p>",
