    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>'Nduja graffiti aubergine</strong> and <strong>roasted pepper</strong> over the<strong> salad</strong></p><p>Top with the<strong> tomatoey croutons </strong>and <strong>cheese shavings</strong></p><p>Spoon over the <strong>crispy 'Nduja </strong>and drizzle over the <strong>basil oil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
